Alan Cox (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Cox_(actor) 0 Alan Douglas Cox (born 6 August 1970) is an English actor. He is perhaps most widely known for portraying a teenage Dr. Watson in Barry Levinson's production Young Sherlock Holmes (1985). Alan_Douglas_Cox ( born_6_August_1970 ) is an_English_actor .
